title: Kumpir Queen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Pizza, Fast food, Take-out, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small family owned take-away with a casual atmosphere has a few seats inside. Falafels, seitan and vegan sauce are made-in-house. Daily vegan choices are falafel doner and pizza. Friday and Saturday serves vegan seitan doner.
